WEBVTT

00:00:02.665 --> 00:00:04.125
Speak up.

00:00:05.209 --> 00:00:07.628
Bring your whole selves to work.

00:00:08.671 --> 00:00:12.175
Be the difference that you want to see.

00:00:13.384 --> 00:00:14.552
Sound familiar?

00:00:15.887 --> 00:00:19.557
Started to sound very familiar
to quite a few employees.

00:00:20.600 --> 00:00:25.772
Now many leaders are asking voices
of difference to speak up.

00:00:26.689 --> 00:00:32.612
And that's because what gets said,
and what doesn't, in our workplaces